Class NewGamePanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • view.NewGamePanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class NewGamePanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.util.Observer
    This class extends a JPanel that is shown according to the BattleshipModel's state by the BattleshipView. This graphic element contains various JPanels, JButtons and JRadioButtons, so that the user can easily choose the settings for its Battleship match, such as grid size, ComputerType and difficulty and timer.
